        "id": 276638,
        "name": "MORTAL ENGINE",
        "username": "mortal_engin3",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/ee7513/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2025-10-03T14:26:21.900Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I don‚Äôt want AI on Signal. Why do I need an AI inside a messenger? I see no point even if it‚Äôs for creative writing or whatever, just use your head. And I believe Signal will never implement AI. Machines are getting smarter while humans are getting dumber. I don‚Äôt want to be more dumb. If you really need AI to write something then just use available AI services, and then just copy that and paste it here on Signal.</p>",
