        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/c/43a26b/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2025-10-03T19:45:48.432Z",
        "cooked": "<p>we absolutely do not need more slop. If you need ai to compose a message, just <strong>don‚Äôt</strong>.</p>\n<p>Emails are turning into the following flow with AI: User A uses AI to slopify their 2 sentences into a corporate letter, User B uses AI to unslopify and summarize what the fuck the other person is saying in 62 lines of nonsense.</p>\n<p>The only usable AI in Signal could be a vectorized local search, which would enable contextual search. ( although even fuzzy search could be better than the current one).</p>",
